## Common Questions

**Is Prime membership worth it for the card?**
Math:
- Prime membership: $139/year
- 5% back on $1,400 Amazon spend = $70
- 5% back on $500 Whole Foods = $25
- Prime Video + other benefits = $44+ value

If you spend $1,400+ on Amazon/Whole Foods, it pays for itself.

**Can I use multiple cards?**
Yes:
- Prime Visa for Amazon/Whole Foods (5%)
- Another card for dining/travel (higher rates elsewhere)

**What about business purchases?**
Amazon Business Card offers different rates:
- 5% on Amazon Business purchases ($10K+ annually)
- 90-day payment terms
- Purchase tracking

